OL,3,CMoorcroft Pottery in Stoke-On-Trent
OL,4,Ccloses after more than 100 years
OL,6,FMoorcroft Pottery in Stoke-on-Trent is
OL,7,Fto close after more than 100 years of
OL,8,Fproducing fine art for worldwide
OL,9,Faudiences.
OL,11,FThe company in Burslem announced on
OL,12,Fits website today (April 30th) that
OL,13,Fwith "deep sadness", it would cease
OL,14,Ftrading as of that day.
OL,16,FThey went on to say that it's
OL,17,Fdirectors had instructed Moore
OL,18,FRecovery to assist with placing the
OL,19,Fcompany into voluntary liquidation.
