OL,3,CMoorcroft Pottery in Stoke-On-Trent
OL,4,Ccloses after more than 100 years
OL,6,FOver the years, it's been known for
OL,7,Fcolourful designs, and was appointed
OL,8,Fas Potter to the late Queen Elizabeth
OL,9,Fthe second in 1928.
OL,11,FMoorcroft was also taken into the
OL,12,Fhomes of Leonard A Lauder, President
OL,13,Fof the Estee Lauder cosmetics empire,
OL,14,Fand a man who has one of the largest
OL,15,FMoorcroft collections in the world:
OL,16,Fformer US Presidents and British Prime
OL,17,FMinisters, famous actors and singers.
