OL,3,CMoorcroft Pottery in Stoke-On-Trent
OL,4,Ccloses after more than 100 years
OL,6,FRecently, the firm had been struggling
OL,7,Fwith rising bills and the impact of
OL,8,Fthe cost of living crisis and was
OL,9,Flooking to find a buyer.
OL,11,FThis is the latest blow to the pottery
OL,12,Findustry in Stoke-on-Trent with the
OL,13,FRoyal Stafford, also based in Burslem,
OL,14,Fcalling in administrators in February.
OL,16,FSome of the workers who are losing
OL,17,Ftheir jobs are being supported by the
OL,18,FGMB Union.
