OL,3,CMoorcroft Pottery in Stoke-On-Trent
OL,4,Ccloses after more than 100 years
OL,6,FGMB Union, Organiser, Chris Hoofe
OL,7,Fsaid: "The closure of Moorcroft is
OL,8,Fdevastating news for workers and their
OL,9,Ffamilies, but unfortunately, it's not
OL,10,Fa surprise.
OL,12,F"The high cost of energy is crippling
OL,13,Fthe ceramics sector in the UK and has
OL,14,Fdirectly led to the loss of 57 jobs at
OL,15,FMoorcroft.
OL,17,F"The Government must act and act now
OL,18,Fto support the ceramics sector and
OL,19,Fprotect workers in this sector."
